OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,F"Sporadic household clusters of
OL,7,Fmeningitis" could appear over the next
OL,8,Ffour weeks in other parts of the UK
OL,9,Flinked to the travel of people away
OL,10,Ffrom Kent, a health leader has
OL,11,Fconfirmed.
OL,13,FKent County Council's director of
OL,14,Fpublic health Dr Anjan Ghosh told a
OL,15,Fbriefing three scenarios were being
OL,16,Flooked at over the next four weeks,
OL,17,Fwith the most likely being that
OL,18,Fstudents who have travelled away from
OL,19,FKent will "incubate" the bug and there
OL,20,Fcould be "household" cases elsewhere.
OL,26,@{D@KOU{D@TO]|D@JOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
