CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FHowever, he said these would be
OL,7,F"containable".
OL,9,FIt comes as the UK Health Security
OL,10,FAgency (UKHSA) said the number of
OL,11,Fcases linked to the outbreak has
OL,12,Freached 29, up from 27 previously.
OL,14,FSome 18 cases have been confirmed,
OL,15,Falongside a further 11 "probable
OL,16,Fcases" ` all with links to Kent, the
OL,17,FUKHSA said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]wD@XOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
