OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FDr Ghosh told the briefing that three
OL,7,F"rough" scenarios are being modelled
OL,8,Ffor the next four weeks, as "that's
OL,9,Fthe time it takes for this whole thing
OL,10,Freally subside.
OL,12,F"The first scenario is that the
OL,13,Foutbreak remains contained in Kent.
OL,15,F"Second scenario is that there are
OL,16,Fpeople who've left, they've gone off
OL,17,Fcampus, and many of them don't stay in
OL,18,FKent, they go and stay elsewhere," Dr
OL,19,FGhosh said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@GO]pD@]OUwD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,F"They were incubating when they left,
OL,7,Fand then they become cases, and there
OL,8,Fare small household, sporadic clusters
OL,9,Foutside of Kent."
OL,11,FHe stressed these cases would be
OL,12,F"containable".
OL,14,FThe third scenario, described by Dr
OL,15,FGhosh as the "worst-case scenario",
OL,16,Fwould result in another cluster
OL,17,Foutside of Kent.
OL,19,FHowever, he said this is "highly
OL,20,Funlikely", with the second scenario
OL,21,F"most likely to be the case".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]tD@AOUtD@MO]wD@NOUwD@bO]{D@
OL,26,AZOU|D@IO]}D@AOU}D@\O]
