OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FThirteen of the 18 cases confirmed by
OL,7,FUKHSA are menB.
OL,9,FAll cases have required hospital
OL,10,Fadmission.
OL,12,FEd Waller, deputy chief executive of
OL,13,FNHS Kent and Medway, said a request
OL,14,Fwas made on Friday for a further 5,000
OL,15,Fdoses of vaccine.
OL,17,FMr Waller told the media briefing:
OL,18,F"6,500 doses of vaccine have been
OL,19,Fdelivered to Kent and Medway from the
OL,20,Fnational stock. There was a request
OL,21,Ftoday for a further 5,000."
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
