PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FMr Waller told reporters that the
OL,7,Fadvice to people queueing is to "just
OL,8,Fthink about where they go".
OL,10,F"As I said, the queue at the other
OL,11,Fsite in Canterbury is shorter at the
OL,12,Fmoment," he added.
OL,14,F"The other two sites are operating `
OL,15,Fthey're less busy than this one. So,
OL,16,Fwe will see as many of the people who
OL,17,Fare in the queue as we can today.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@ZO]rD@AOUtD@HO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
