PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FWhen asked about the closing times of
OL,7,Fthe vaccine centres, he said: "We are
OL,8,Ftrying to maximise the capacity and
OL,9,Fthe opening hours of all the sites.
OL,11,F"So we are in the process of
OL,12,Foperationalising as much capacity as
OL,13,Fwe can."
OL,15,FIt comes as four schools in Kent say
OL,16,Fthey have confirmed or suspected cases
OL,17,Fof meningitis among their pupils, as
OL,18,FWes Streeting said sixth form students
OL,19,Fand pupils should continue to attend
OL,20,Fschools.
OL,26,@oD@_OUsD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
