PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FThe headteacher at Queen Elizabeth's
OL,7,FGrammar School in Faversham paid
OL,8,Ftribute on Monday to a year 13 pupil
OL,9,Fnamed locally as Juliette Kenny, who
OL,10,Fdied at the weekend from the infection.
OL,12,FA student at the university of Kent
OL,13,Fhas also died, and Canterbury Christ
OL,14,FChurch University has also confirmed a
OL,15,Fcase of meningitis among its students.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
