OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Mr Streeting said
OL,7,Fstudents at schools who visited the
OL,8,FClub Chemistry nightclub or who have
OL,9,Fhad close contact with the infection
OL,10,Fshould attend sites for antibiotics,
OL,11,Fbut they are not advising school
OL,12,Fclosures.
OL,14,FThe four schools that reportedly have
OL,15,Fconfirmed or suspected cases currently
OL,16,Fare Queen Elizabeth's Grammar School,
OL,17,FFaversham, Norton Knatchbull School,
OL,18,FAshford, Simon Langton Grammar School
OL,19,Ffor Boys, in Canterbury, and The
OL,20,FCanterbury Academy, in Canterbury.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
