OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FHighworth Grammar School in Ashford
OL,7,Fsaid on Tuesday a year 13 pupil had
OL,8,Fbeen admitted to hospital with a
OL,9,Fsuspected case of meningitis.
OL,11,FOn Friday headteacher Duncan Beer said
OL,12,Fthe student had tested negative.
OL,14,FIt had also been reported a year 13
OL,15,Fstudent at Dane Court Grammar School
OL,16,Fin Broadstairs also had the infection,
OL,17,Fbut the school has since said the case
OL,18,Fis not confirmed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
