PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774185071
OL,3,C'Sporadic' household clusters of
OL,4,Cmeningitis could appear elsewhere in UK
OL,6,FKent County Council has confirmed all
OL,7,Fits mainstream schools are open as
OL,8,Fnormal.
OL,10,FTwo specialist school were closed as a
OL,11,Fprecaution on Tuesday - Nore Academy,
OL,12,Fa special school (SEMH), and the co-
OL,13,Fjoined alternative provision Estuary
OL,14,FAcademy Island.
OL,16,FThe council confirmed on Wednesday
OL,17,Fthese have both reopened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
